thread.title: JASMINE
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by JASMINE

author: JASMINE
title: JASMINE
text:
After arriving at the Gold Coast airport my husband and I decided to rent a car.
We first spoke to another car rental place who was going to charge us $350 we decided to have a look around thinking this was about the going rate
We spoke to a few more then found redspot which was the cheapest for us great car no trouble with it or with the staff. Have to pay a $200 deposit got it back the next week fantastic highly recommended
